      "text": "いつまでも名前呼ばれながら逃げてたら目立つでしょ！\n私が立ち止まってあげたのよ。用件は何？　早くして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you keep calling my name while running away‚ I'll stand out\nI stopped for you. What's your business? Tell me quickly",
