      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "実は、雫と一緒に映画を見るはずだったのですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I was planning to watch a movie with Shizuku‚ but",
