      "text": "（子供向けと言いつつ、めちゃくちゃ泣ける内容で）\n（思わずハマっちゃったのよね。衣装のセンスもいいし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even though it's for kids‚ the story is incredibly emotional）\n（So I got hooked on it. The sense of costume is also good）",
